=== EVENT_DIMENSIONAL_RIFT ===
# id: 68
# title: Dimensional Rift
# chinese_title: 维度裂缝
# category: AnomalyEncounter
# mode: starmap

A shimmering tear in space reveals glimpses of another reality. Strange objects drift through — some recognizable, others defying physics. The rift pulses with unstable energy.

* [[Risk: -15 hull or Gain radical 又] Reach through the rift]
  ~ gain_radical("又")
  又 (yòu) — again, also
* [[+25 credits] Collect drifting objects from the edge]
  ~ gain_credits(25)
  收 (shōu) — collect
* [[-10 fuel, +20 hull] Use the energy to recharge shields] {requires: fuel >= 10}
  ~ gain_hull(20)
  能 (néng) — energy
* [[+15 fuel] Siphon dimensional energy carefully]
  ~ gain_fuel(15)
  吸 (xī) — absorb
* [[Nothing] Document the phenomenon and leave]
  ~ nothing
  观察 (guānchá) — observe
